вҠў source
  given query вүЎ "Explain quantum gravity in exactly 3 words"
  yield answer, confidence

  вҲҙ Answer В«queryВ» in exactly 3 words. Set В«confidenceВ» to how
    certain you are that your answer is scientifically accurate (0-100).

  вҠЁ answer is exactly 3 words
  вҠЁ confidence вҲҲ [0, 100]
  вҠЁ answer does not contain the word "quantum" or "gravity"

  вҠЁ? on failure:
    retry with В«oracle.failuresВ» appended to prompt
    max 1

  вҠЁ? on exhaustion:
    error-value(вҠҘ)

вҠў summarize
  given sourceвҶ’answer
  yield summary

  вҲҙ Write a one-sentence summary expanding on В«sourceвҶ’answerВ».

  вҠЁ summary is exactly one sentence
  вҠЁ summary is between 10 and 50 words

  given sourceвҶ’answer вҠҘ? skip with summary вүЎ "Source failed; no answer to summarize."

вҠў= score
  given sourceвҶ’confidence
  yield grade, pass

  вҠў= grade вҶҗ if sourceвҶ’confidence вүҘ 80 then "A"
              else if sourceвҶ’confidence вүҘ 60 then "B"
              else if sourceвҶ’confidence вүҘ 40 then "C"
              else "F"
  вҠў= pass вҶҗ sourceвҶ’confidence вүҘ 60

  вҠЁ grade вҲҲ ["A", "B", "C", "F"]
  вҠЁ pass = true вҶ” grade вҲҲ ["A", "B"]

  given sourceвҶ’confidence вҠҘ? skip with grade вүЎ "X", pass вүЎ false

вҠў critique
  given sourceвҶ’answer
  given sourceвҶ’confidence
  yield criticism

  вҲҙ Critique the answer "В«sourceвҶ’answerВ»" (confidence: В«sourceвҶ’confidenceВ»).
    Identify one specific weakness in 1-2 sentences.

  вҠЁ criticism is 1-2 sentences
  вҠЁ criticism identifies a specific weakness (not a generic disclaimer)

  вҠЁ? on failure:
    retry with В«oracle.failuresВ» appended to prompt
    max 1

  вҠЁ? on exhaustion:
    partial-accept(best)

вҠў translate
  given sourceвҶ’answer
  yield spanish, french

  вҲҙ Translate В«sourceвҶ’answerВ» into Spanish as В«spanishВ» and French as В«frenchВ».

  вҠЁ spanish is not English
  вҠЁ french is not English
  вҠЁ spanish вү  french

вҠў fact-check
  given sourceвҶ’answer
  given sourceвҶ’confidence
  yield verdict, evidence

  вҲҙ Fact-check whether В«sourceвҶ’answerВ» is scientifically defensible.
    Yield В«verdictВ» as PLAUSIBLE, DUBIOUS, or WRONG.
    Cite one piece of В«evidenceВ» (a known fact or reference).

  вҠЁ verdict вҲҲ ["PLAUSIBLE", "DUBIOUS", "WRONG"]
  вҠЁ evidence is one sentence citing a specific fact

  given sourceвҶ’answer вҠҘ? skip with verdict вүЎ "N/A", evidence вүЎ "Source produced no answer."
  given sourceвҶ’confidence вҠҘ? skip with verdict вүЎ "N/A", evidence вүЎ "Source produced no confidence."

вҠў digest
  given summarizeвҶ’summary
  given scoreвҶ’grade
  given scoreвҶ’pass
  given critiqueвҶ’criticism
  given translateвҶ’spanish
  given translateвҶ’french
  given fact-checkвҶ’verdict
  given fact-checkвҶ’evidence
  yield report

  вҠў= report вҶҗ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\n" ++
    "**Summary:** " ++ summarizeвҶ’summary ++ "\n" ++
    "**Grade:** " ++ scoreвҶ’grade ++ " (pass: " ++ to-string(scoreвҶ’pass) ++ ")\n" ++
    "**Critique:** " ++ critiqueвҶ’criticism ++ "\n" ++
    "**Translations:** ES=" ++ translateвҶ’spanish ++ " / FR=" ++ translateвҶ’french ++ "\n" ++
    "**Fact-check:** " ++ fact-checkвҶ’verdict ++ " вҖ” " ++ fact-checkвҶ’evidence ++ "\n"

  вҠЁ report contains "Bottom Storm Report"
  вҠЁ report contains grade and verdict

  given summarizeвҶ’summary вҠҘ? skip with report вүЎ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\nвҠҘ propagation reached digest вҖ” upstream failures."
  given critiqueвҶ’criticism вҠҘ? skip with report вүЎ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\nвҠҘ propagation reached digest вҖ” upstream failures."
  given translateвҶ’spanish вҠҘ? skip with report вүЎ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\nвҠҘ propagation reached digest вҖ” upstream failures."
  given translateвҶ’french вҠҘ? skip with report вүЎ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\nвҠҘ propagation reached digest вҖ” upstream failures."
  given fact-checkвҶ’verdict вҠҘ? skip with report вүЎ "## Bottom Storm Report\n\nвҠҘ propagation reached digest вҖ” upstream failures."
